Public Sub CloseCanvasEngine()

    On Error Resume Next

    'Kill the canvas host (new sub by KSNiloc!)
    Call CNVKillCanvasHost(App.hInstance, canvasHost)

    'Shutdown the canvas engine
    Call CNVShutdown

    'Shutdown the FreeImage library
    Call CloseImage

